[0;31m[0m[0;31m-# Note that "password" sends passwords in clear text; "md5" or[0m
[0;31m[0m[0;31m-# "scram-sha-256" are preferred since they send encrypted passwords.[0m
[0;31m[0m[0;31m-#[0m
[0;31m[0m[0;31m-# OPTIONS are a set of options for the authentication in the format[0m
